headline.main: Yemen Retakes Oil Export Terminal From Al Qaeda

keywords.value: Al Qaeda in the Arabian Peninsula
keywords.name: organizations

snippet: Yemeni forces and allies from the United Arab Emirates regained control of the Ash Shihr terminal on Monday from Al Qaeda in the Arabian Peninsula.
lead_paragraph: Yemeni forces and allies from the United Arab Emirates regained control of the Ash Shihr terminal on Monday from Al Qaeda in the Arabian Peninsula.
